msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB"
msgstr "Mark / Align PCB"

msgid "为产品定义 **Mark 点** 与 **独特标记**，让系统在每次检测前都能稳定定位 PCB 的实际位置："
msgstr "Define a product's **Mark Points** and **Unique Markers** so the system can reliably locate the actual PCB position before every inspection:"

msgid "**Mark 点（参考标记）**：补偿来料偏移与拼板单元之间的微小错位。"
msgstr "**Mark Points (reference marks)**: compensate for incoming-board shift and small misalignment between sub-boards in an array."

msgid "**独特标记（Unique Marker）**：在 A/B 面双产品检测中自动区分两块不同的 PCB。"
msgstr "**Unique Markers**: automatically distinguish two different PCBs in A/B-side mixed-product inspection."

msgid "如何进入"
msgstr "How to open it"

msgid "进入产品的 :guilabel:`产品编程页面（Teach）`，点击顶部第一个标签页 :guilabel:`标记 / 对齐 PCB`。"
msgstr "Open a product's :guilabel:`Teach` page, then click the first top tab, :guilabel:`Mark / Align PCB`."

msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB 主界面：左侧标记列表 + 中央 PCB 画布"
msgstr "Mark / Align PCB main view: marker list on the left, PCB canvas in the center."

msgid "Mark 点（参考标记点）"
msgstr "Mark Points (reference marks)"

msgid "点击工具栏的 :guilabel:`+ 标记`，在拍摄图像上框选 PCB 上固定、易识别的参考标记点（圆形 mark、矩形 mark、或复杂的丝印图案均可）。绘制完成后会出现在左侧标记列表中。"
msgstr "Click :guilabel:`+ Mark` on the toolbar, then drag on the captured image to box a stable, easy-to-recognize reference mark on the PCB (a circular mark, a rectangular mark, or a complex silkscreen pattern). The new mark appears in the marker list on the left."

msgid "标记形状（Shape Type）"
msgstr "Shape Type"

msgid "每个 mark 点支持三种定位方式。优先用 AI 算法（圆形 / 矩形），失败时再退到模板匹配："
msgstr "Each Mark Point supports three ways to be located. Prefer the AI algorithm (Circle / Rectangle); fall back to template matching when it fails:"

msgid "形状类型"
msgstr "Shape type"

msgid "定位原理"
msgstr "How it locates"

msgid "何时使用"
msgstr "When to use"

msgid "**圆形标记 (Circle)**"
msgstr "**Circle Marker**"

msgid "AI 算法在图像中搜索 **圆形** 特征来定位"
msgstr "An AI algorithm searches the image for a **circular** feature."

msgid "mark 为圆形，首选"
msgstr "Mark is circular — preferred."

msgid "**矩形标记 (Rectangle)**"
msgstr "**Rectangle Marker**"

msgid "AI 算法在图像中搜索 **矩形** 特征来定位"
msgstr "An AI algorithm searches the image for a **rectangular** feature."

msgid "mark 为矩形，首选"
msgstr "Mark is rectangular — preferred."

msgid "**模板标记 (Template)**"
msgstr "**Template Marker**"

msgid "把框内图像存为 **模板**，检测时用模板匹配找最相似的位置"
msgstr "Stores the image inside the box as a **template**, then uses template matching to find the most similar spot at inspection time."

msgid "mark 不规则，或表面有油墨 / 氧化 / 反光导致 AI 失败时的退路"
msgstr "A fallback when the mark is irregular, or when ink / oxidation / glare on its surface makes the AI fail."

msgid "模板标记对旋转、缩放、光照变化比 AI 算法更敏感，要求 mark 外观稳定；因此 **优先圆形 / 矩形，AI 失败再改模板标记**。"
msgstr "Template matching is more sensitive to rotation, scaling, and lighting changes than the AI algorithm and needs a stable mark appearance; so **prefer Circle / Rectangle, and switch to Template Marker only when the AI fails**."

msgid "其他属性"
msgstr "Other options"

msgid "**二值化抽色（Mark Binarization）**：mark 点底色不稳定时启用，先把 mark 抽成二值掩膜再匹配。开启后会出现 **三色范围** 参数（X / Y / Z / A），点击 :guilabel:`显示色范围 Mask` 可实时预览抽色效果。"
msgstr "**Mark Binarization**: enable when the mark's background color is unstable; the mark is reduced to a binary mask before matching. Enabling it exposes a **Tricolor range** (X / Y / Z / A); click :guilabel:`Show Color Range Mask` to preview the binarization live."

msgid "**定位（Locate）**：让相机移动到当前 mark 点的金板位置，便于核对位置是否正确。"
msgstr "**Locate**: move the camera to this Mark Point's golden-board position to verify the location is correct."

msgid "**预测中心（Predict Center）**：系统重新分析框内图像，自动微调 mark 点中心，消除手画时的轻微偏差。"
msgstr "**Predict Center**: re-analyzes the image inside the box and auto-adjusts the Mark Point's center, removing the slight drift of a hand-drawn box."

msgid "**精修（Refine）**：手动微调 mark 点框的位置与大小。"
msgstr "**Refine**: manually fine-tune the Mark Point box's position and size."

msgid "二维定位需要 **2 个 mark 点**，分别置于 PCB 的对角位置。当前版本 **最多 2 个**，不能再添加更多。"
msgstr "2D alignment needs **two Mark Points**, one in each opposite corner of the PCB. The current release **supports at most 2** — no more can be added."

msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB 画布上的 mark 点位置示意"
msgstr "Mark Point placement on the Mark / Align PCB canvas"

msgid "独特标记（Unique Marker）"
msgstr "Unique Marker"

msgid "仅在 **A/B 面双产品检测** 场景下需要。点击 :guilabel:`+ 独特标记`，在每个产品上框选一处与另一面差异明显的区域（例如缺口、专属丝印、特殊器件），该区域将作为产品识别特征。"
msgstr "Only needed for **A/B-side mixed-product inspection**. Click :guilabel:`+ Unique Marker`, then box an area on each product that is visibly different from the other side (a notch, a unique silkscreen, a one-of-a-kind component); this area becomes the product's identification feature."

msgid "独特标记支持三种 **分类方法**："
msgstr "A Unique Marker supports three **classification methods**:"

msgid "分类方法"
msgstr "Method"

msgid "原理"
msgstr "How it works"

msgid "适合场景"
msgstr "Best for"

msgid "**GENERIC**"
msgstr "**GENERIC**"

msgid "通用 AI 分类器"
msgstr "General-purpose AI classifier"

msgid "大多数差异明显的场景"
msgstr "Most cases where the products differ obviously"

msgid "**OCV**"
msgstr "**OCV**"

msgid "基于字符外观对比"
msgstr "Compares character appearance"

msgid "两个产品有不同但相近的丝印文字"
msgstr "Two products with different but similar silkscreen text"

msgid "**OCR**"
msgstr "**OCR**"

msgid "基于字符识别"
msgstr "Character recognition"

msgid "字符清晰、可读"
msgstr "Text is clear and legible"

msgid "每个产品在 A/B 面模式下需要 **正好一个** 独特标记。若所选区域在两面区分度不足，启动检测时系统会返回 **HTTP 428** 错误并提示重选区域。"
msgstr "In A/B-side mode each product needs **exactly one** Unique Marker. If the chosen region is not distinctive enough between the two sides, starting inspection returns **HTTP 428** and prompts you to re-select the area."

msgid "使用建议与常见问题"
msgstr "Tips and common issues"

msgid "**常见 Mark 点定位问题与处理：**"
msgstr "**Common Mark Point issues and fixes:**"

msgid "**检测时找不到 Mark 点、报错退出**：先切到 AI 算法（圆形 / 矩形）更稳定；若表面有油墨、氧化、污渍导致 AI 找圆失败，改用 **模板标记**。"
msgstr "**Mark Point not found at inspection time, aborts with an error**: first switch to the AI algorithm (Circle / Rectangle) — it is more robust; if ink, oxidation, or contamination makes the AI circle finder fail, switch to **Template Marker**."

msgid "**找到了但定位不准 / 误报多**：检查板子是否放反（对称 mark 可能巧合找到但定位错误）；两个 mark 点都画在稳定不易磨损处，且尽量分布在对角，利于精确解算旋转角。"
msgstr "**Found but localization is off / many false positives**: check whether the board was loaded reversed (symmetric marks can be found in the wrong place by coincidence); put both Mark Points on stable, wear-resistant spots, as far apart as possible (near opposite corners) so the rotation angle resolves precisely."

msgid "**AB 面切换后找不到 Mark 点**：先确认板子方向；若单测 B 面能找到、AB 一起测找不到，多半是独特标记区分度不足，回本页重选差异更明显的区域。"
msgstr "**Mark Point not found after switching A/B side**: first confirm the board orientation; if side B alone is found but mixed A/B fails, the Unique Marker is most likely not distinctive enough — return to this page and re-select a more clearly different area."

msgid "**热板 / 冷板差异导致间歇误报**：在元件配置中适当放大 **允许偏移距离** 与 **允许旋转角度**，吸收温度形变。"
msgstr "**Intermittent false positives between hot and cold boards**: in the component configuration, increase **Allowed Shift Distance** and **Allowed Rotation Angle** to absorb thermal deformation."

msgid "**Mark 点选择建议：**"
msgstr "**Mark Point selection guidelines:**"

msgid "优先选 PCB 上 **固定、不易磨损、不易被遮挡** 的圆形或矩形丝印参考点。"
msgstr "Prefer **stable, wear-resistant, unobstructed** circular or rectangular silkscreen reference marks on the PCB."

msgid "避免选 **元件本身**，因为可能贴歪或缺料；也避免 **靠近板边**，拼接时可能被裁切。"
msgstr "Avoid **components themselves** (which may be skewed or missing) and **locations near the board edge** (which can be cropped during stitching)."

msgid "避免选 **对称分布** 的 mark 点（板子放反时可能被错误识别）。"
msgstr "Avoid **symmetrically placed** marks (they can be mis-identified when the board is loaded reversed)."

msgid "每块 PCB 选 **2 个** mark 点（当前上限），分别置于对角，覆盖整板范围。"
msgstr "Pick **2 Mark Points** per PCB (the current ceiling), one in each opposite corner, to span the whole board."

